  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (NC-6 clean)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. All 13 credibility factors are addressed: 12 factors are fully assessed with achievedLevel >= requiredLevel, and 1 factor (Equivalency of input parameters) is designated not-applicable with a detailed, documented rationale explaining why the factor does not apply to this specific COU. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed and linked. Provenance chain is complete. Decision: Accepted.",
