      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions (MMS) applied to the incompressible Navier-Stokes and power-law hemolysis transport equations. Observed convergence rates match theoretical order (2nd-order spatial, 1st-order temporal). All benchmark cases from the ASME V&V 20 suite pass. Code verification level 4 achieved."
