      "rationale": "Quantitative comparison performed using the ASME V&V 20 validation metric. Validation uncertainty (Uval) computed from experimental, numerical, and input uncertainties. For NIH, E/Uval < 1.0 at all 5 operating points, indicating model predictions are within the combined uncertainty band. Output comparison level 4 achieved."
